nz.ac.vuw.pelhamoliv.bugworld

Class BugWorldFX

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.application.Application
      • nz.ac.vuw.pelhamoliv.bugworld.BugWorldFX

  • public class BugWorldFX
extends javafx.application.Application
    SetUp is the class for drawing the user-interface and initializing the world

    Contains two scenes, a start scene, and a simulation scene Start scene is for picking presets for the simulation to run. The Simulation scene runs the simulation and includes buttons to restart, pause, or return to the main menu.

    Author:
    pelhamoliv
